replace in package.json your app-name data

"name"         "app-name",
"productName"  "view-app-name",
"version"      "1.0.0",

replace icons in ./icons and ./build/icons

replace config in main.js

appTheme - default app theme (system, dark, light)
mainPage - 1st page to load
urlWhiteList - list of patterns to access for external resources

1) install modules
npm install 

2) run project
npm start

3) build project
npx electron-builder --win 